  "texts": [
    "Articles published from 2023 onwards were excluded, resulting in the removal of 42 publications.",
    "The focus was then narrowed to peer-reviewed articles, which brought the count down to 2,703.",
    "Further refinement was made by selecting articles from five WoS categories pertinent to the research subject: Education Educational Research, Language Linguistics, Linguistics, Education Scientific Disciplines, and Psychology Educational.",
    "The selection of these categories reduced the pool to 364 articles.",
    "The emphasis on English language articles further narrowed the selection to 345."
  ],
